,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:50:57.000Z","msg":"1. 已立法，但係冇條文，嚇鳩你，所有人自我審查，連外國國旗都唔夠膽舉，<br />\n2. 玩大咗，揾落台階，已立法，但冇條文，搞掂！起碼英國佬話 要睇咗條文 先決定點樣制裁，<br />\n3. 同老美有 deal，條文 老美未批准，"},{"pid":"4e4c1b519e93e7a583f7129702f773f99b906442","tid":2086770,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:54:50.000Z","msg":"【置頂】<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>選戰告急</strong></span></span> 倒數十星期 立即十星期拉票行動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2082608\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2082608</a><br />\n大家覺唔覺已被共匪立法引哂去，無人理9月6呢！"},{"pid":"268741c73d55f1d4c227b31c8e16911ca57472cc","tid":2086770,"uid":275425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45ee9b0b28fd0ecbbc96a6a51492d80f4736824a","tid":2086770,"uid":244361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d73b9c333a9089b0b06d02c51e954f468462c699","tid":2086770,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:04:58.000Z","msg":"無條文西方就難有動作（好似係）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:15:43.000Z","msg":"我都覺得係<br />\n<br />\n但又想阻嚇人聽日出黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:01:33.000Z","msg":"但係而家完全唔知做乜鳩。10點啦喎，真係要等2359？"},{"pid":"5a8742848ae1290088ac1da8cf67921cb62a632d","tid":2086770,"uid":18296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:02:19.000Z","msg":"我覺得係象徵意味多, 想23年回歸日推出國安法, 美其名二次回歸<br />\n浪漫主意啫"},{"pid":"3744b76f0ba67f349bec548ae570784eee13cf7f","tid":2086770,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d73b9c333a9089b0b06d02c51e954f468462c699","tid":2086770,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:04:58.000Z","msg":"無條文西方就難有動作（好似係）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:04:01.000Z","msg":"呢個只係一廂情願既諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"320cfa2bd8e569c8c7a4d70f319a46ce998c2a8d","tid":2086770,"uid":279585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime